  "title": "A cigar shaped UFO was spotted hovering over Boqueirão in Curitiba-PR [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/a-cigar-shaped-ufo-was-spotted-hovering-over-boqueirao-in-curitiba-pr-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1at",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 25th, 1996</strong>. Time: 10h15 am. Duration: 1 minute. A military man in São José dos Pinhais, State of Paraná, along with two other people, spotted an unidentified flying object, shaped like a &#8220;cigar&#8221; and with the size of a &#8220;Boeing 707&#8221;. According to the witnesses, the UFO was silver in color and initially remained stationary, &#8220;stopped, and then started [a] rapid descent until it disappeared&#8221;. The UFO was seen with the naked eye and in a clear night, about 1,000ft above the Barracks of Boqueirão.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.429. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de São José dos Pinhais, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
